### Health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/healthz

### Machine status (auth required)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/machine/status
X-API-Key: local-admin-key

### Create project
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/projects
X-API-Key: local-admin-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "demo",
  "repo": "https://github.com/example/repo.git",
  "environment": "dev",
  "namespace": "ns-a",
  "cpuLimit": "1000m",
  "memoryLimit": "1024Mi",
  "serviceAccount": "deployer-sa"
}

### Create service
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/services
X-API-Key: local-admin-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": 1,
  "name": "api",
  "image": "registry.example.com/demo/api",
  "replicas": 2
}

### Enqueue command (dry-run)
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/commands
X-API-Key: local-admin-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": 1,
  "action": "delete",
  "kind": "deployment",
  "name": "api",
  "dryRun": true
}

### Enqueue command apply
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/commands
X-API-Key: local-admin-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": 1,
  "action": "create",
  "manifest": "apiVersion: apps/v1\nkind: Deployment\nmetadata:\n  name: api\nspec:\n  replicas: 1\n  selector:\n    matchLabels:\n      app: api\n  template:\n    metadata:\n      labels:\n        app: api\n    spec:\n      containers:\n        - name: api\n          image: nginx:1.27\n          resources:\n            limits:\n              cpu: 500m\n              memory: 256Mi\n"
}

### Enqueue build/deploy
POST http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/builds
X-API-Key: local-admin-key
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "projectId": 1,
  "serviceId": 1,
  "gitRef": "main"
}

### Check job
GET http://127.0.0.1:8080/api/v1/jobs/job-123
X-API-Key: local-admin-key
